{"tid":2348482,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人若變呢年好撚慘","createTime":"2020-12-31T17:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T07:44:52.000Z","uid":307910,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9e7c8383746ea97480f2c4a7c628f5f01bdc5e5e","tid":2348482,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:11:16.000Z","msg":"我係呢一年咩都冇晒<br />\n係真係咩都無晒<br />\n唔係淨係kelly咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n我呢一年真係過得好棘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本以為有啲人可以幫到我，扶返自己起身，點知原來全世界都係講利益，唔講感情。<br />\n無咗就係無咗，我嚟緊嘅人生應該都唔會過得好順利，我先明白原來呢個世界真係要靠自己。<br />\n<br />\n嗰啲我對你好而你又俾鑊杰嘢我嘆嘅人，自己好自為之<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔掛住kelly，唔好再話鬧得我好啱，好撚凍 今晚早抖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7754438b7b769fce58579c57f6c3b8fe1edb2348","tid":2348482,"uid":305799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:16:51.000Z","msg":"jelly呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0fb572180b6e7e4b020ea49d45903cd1d40bc1","tid":2348482,"uid":369015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />jelly我真係好掛住你"},{"pid":"2ad3b2afa54d574dc94204179125aae41d14b51e","tid":2348482,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7754438b7b769fce58579c57f6c3b8fe1edb2348","tid":2348482,"uid":305799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:16:51.000Z","msg":"jelly呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:34:40.000Z","msg":"呢個係乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e94d47ad375e7802b32854dd683b3b15397340c","tid":2348482,"uid":305799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ad3b2afa54d574dc94204179125aae41d14b51e","tid":2348482,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":1,